<br>
Got my epic armor.... <br>
<br>
My con is GROSSLY capped!!! <br>
<br>
I had to take off 59 con worth of Equipment, in order to drop my con 9 points.... <br>
<br>
It is just that everything that seems to have Charima on it, is also +con.. <br>
<br>
MY &quot;accessories&quot;: <br>
Ring of Haorfrost <br>
Some DF ring with resists and 24 hps <br>
2 Infernal Black Diamond Bracers <br>
Cloak of the Unseen Stalker <br>
Some DF Necklace that is +7 cha (and con) <br>
Belt of con/dex/qui <br>
Snow Diamond 81 hps... <br>
<br>
I am sitting at: <br>
0 Crush resist <br>
9 slash <br>
19 thrust <br>
anywhere between 9 and 23 spell resists... <br>
<br>
what can i do to complete up my equipment, and not have wasted con..  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ukjeld.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kjeld</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 84<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/23/02 4:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hmm</span><hr size=1> Aye epics stats are pretty disappointing, except from the great sleeves <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Some possible choices : <br>
- Jade Moonshone cloak or cloak of the Dragonwolf from Malmo. Both are excellent.<br>
- Band of Ice (insanely rare ring unfortunately, off wraiths and wights in raumarik and jamtland). There is a good ring from spin with nice resists too.<br>
- the sapphire belt from DF (melee resists, yumm)<br>
- ditch your diamond DF bracers and use the cha7 spirit6% heat6% bracers from spindehella, you'll lose 6 cha, but, considering your con and str are capped, you'll lose nothing else and gain a total of 24% resistance against common mez/stun magic  types<br>
- ditch your sapphire necklace (cha7 str10 con10) in favor of the diamond one (with hps and 6% to 3 resists among which thrust)<br>
<br>
Basically, whatever you'll wear, you'll lose some points in charisma, unfortunately, because the charisma items have often wasted strength and  constitution stats. However, epic armor resistances are pitifull (vast downgrade from whatever diamon/sapphire/rauma/malmo armor people wear in their 40ies), and you need to fix that imho. The jewel from DF (cha15 hp 51 - let that 81hp jewel to tanks, there are other items available to max yer hps) and the princess gauntlets (cha 1<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> , or maybe the 10 cha belt from the grand chancellor can re-balance your charisma a bit, while allowing to use other slots for high resistance-low stats items (though ditching epic gloves resistances is a tough call).<br>
<br>
I have not found myself a definite answer. The way our epic armor is poorly balanced (low cha, low resists, too much strength and constitution), ya'll have to either go for charisma and waste con/str overcap or go for resists and keep low cha.<br>
Seems spellcrafters will soon have a lot of work <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.showPrevMessage?topicID=31.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.showNextMessage?topicID=31.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.emailToFriend?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.threadControl?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm9.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://p